with all your defects.

725
01:00:12,277 --> 01:00:14,212
You wanted to see me?

726
01:00:17,081 --> 01:00:19,250
You know when I was here last?

727
01:00:20,417 --> 01:00:21,718
No.

728
01:00:21,919 --> 01:00:24,521
Neither do I.
Beautiful, isn't it?

729
01:00:28,658 --> 01:00:31,694
