You need to get some sleep.

824
01:10:05,959 --> 01:10:10,597
I'm only tired when my eyes are open.
When they're closed, I just feel...

825
01:10:10,797 --> 01:10:12,599
scared.

826
01:10:13,933 --> 01:10:15,468
