852
01:13:08,160 --> 01:13:10,296
Thank you, darling.

853
01:13:44,127 --> 01:13:46,329
Did you really like it?

854
01:13:47,497 --> 01:13:49,266
I loved it.

855
01:13:50,633 --> 01:13:52,602
But do you think it's commercial?

856
01:13:53,236 --> 01:13:57,073
People always buy Tobias's novels
whether or not they read them.

857
01:13:57,974 --> 01:14:01,176
It's the nice thing
about being an icon.

858
01:14:07,315 --> 01:14:09,351
