865
01:14:36,375 --> 01:14:38,010
I...

866
01:14:39,712 --> 01:14:42,181
just wanted to...

867
01:14:43,048 --> 01:14:46,952
tell you how grateful
I am to both of you.

868
01:14:48,887 --> 01:14:53,158
